00:37:34.110 --> 00:37:37.690
At any rate, so can you discuss,
interpret, a little

00:37:37.690 --> 00:37:41.310
bit, this graph,
this equation?

00:37:41.310 --> 00:37:42.680
What is it telling us?

00:37:42.680 --> 00:37:52.414
What is it telling us that
